{"tid":2152360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"西貢搜遊艇 錄影稱無電 打指模無墨  黎智英折騰三差館終獲釋","createTime":"2020-08-12T02:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T02:56:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3c16f5b94a6dff1d1790a30d27f8fd8e4a3e0e86","tid":2152360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:51:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/R3VRI5C2L3JB73CJH57EXKRNPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FR3VRI5C2L3JB73CJH57EXKRNPY%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=1f5cdf0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FR3VRI5C2L3JB73CJH57EXKRNPY%2F&h=0f5701df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/R3VRI5C2L3JB73CJH57EXKRNPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n西貢搜遊艇 錄影稱無電 打指模無墨 <br />\n黎智英折騰三差館終獲釋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【瘋狂搜捕】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉嫌違反國安法及串謀欺詐等罪名被捕的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，前日扣留旺角警署一晚後，昨晨被帶到西貢遊艇會，登上其中一艘遊艇協助調查，離開遊艇會時被記者問及在警署狀況，他豁達地說：「都係咁啦，捱得到嘅！」據悉，警方昨午一度以電力故障為由，將黎轉送西九龍警察總部進行錄影會面；又以旺角警署印台無墨為由，送黎往油麻地警署打指模。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨10時55分，72歲的黎智英被帶離旺角警署，直接駛去西貢香港遊艇會，。。。。。。。。。。，登上遊艇，全程有律師陪同，只見黎智英精神不錯，氣定神閒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lgqw38RObrtDQjA7Ee3nuvllalQ=/640x457/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4E2JYW35WDQFXWSNCAAAY4RNEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Flgqw38RObrtDQjA7Ee3nuvllalQ%3D%2F640x457%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4E2JYW35WDQFXWSNCAAAY4RNEM.jpg&h=cd8d28da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英獲准保釋，在律師陪同下離開旺角警署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎回應扣署：捱得到嘅<br />\n<br />\n警員在遊艇外拍照，並向遊艇會職員查問，其後登上遊艇搜證約35分鐘後離開。黎被帶上車前，記者追問他前晚在警署狀況，他邊行邊說：「都係咁啦，捱得到嘅！」。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至下午3時20分，黎智英再被帶離旺角警署，登上警車，被送往西九龍警察總部，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上9時左右，黎的兩名代表律師及民主黨前主席何俊仁陪同下，在旺角警。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，黎的次子黎耀恩被通宵扣查逾30小時後，至昨晚約7時半獲准保釋，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fGnaDix3hMhBTeGC7EHf0ciqbIU=/640x389/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BRYCVARCBSU5RIOGJEVFFZJI3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfGnaDix3hMhBTeGC7EHf0ciqbIU%3D%2F640x389%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBRYCVARCBSU5RIOGJEVFFZJI3M.jpg&h=c4d448e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多名市民手持《蘋果日報》在警署外為黎智英打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至今未有人被落案起訴<br />\n<br />\n警方國安處連同刑事處人員，前日展開大規模拘捕行動，先後以違反港版國安法及串謀欺詐等罪名，先後在不同地區拘捕黎智。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，本案有部份壹傳媒人員的資產被凍結，至今未有人被落案起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RpgC7CVRg_r__hFm3ghINejdW-4=/488x868/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XZV5GOCRFAU7AJ5NITWPEJDX3Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRpgC7CVRg_r__hFm3ghINejdW-4%3D%2F488x868%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXZV5GOCRFAU7AJ5NITWPEJDX3Q.gif&h=43247f12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0b7545e93abd99dcaa1f90048dc51854cf61046","tid":2152360,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至今未有人被落案起訴。</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}